review.comment: Thanks Ruby, Michaela, Kate & Susy for helping me get my work visa. You really showed why you're the best migration team in the country! If anyone has any doubts about which migration agency to choose, go with AIA. As a premium migration agency you can trust them and you can rest assured that they will look after you.

Thanks for helping to bring my partner over to Australia! In hindsight I totally would have stuffed up the application if I tried to do it myself. You showed me the documentation and evidences required which I never would have thought of myself. And you took the time to write a submission letter to the immigration department. You really do go the extra mile.

AIA you really are fantastic! Having an employer willing to sponsor me was great until I realised they didn't know how to handle the immigration process. I'll never regret my decision to contact you and get your help. You enabled my employer to become registered and for me to get my work visa. Even though I had a lot of hoops to jump through, you simplified it for me and were there for me every step of the way. Thank you!

Thank you for helping me get my visa. I was struggling with all the options and you made it really simple and clear for me. Your advice was top quality and helped me have a future in Australia. More than anything, you were friendly and caring. You actually took the time to listen to me and my situation and identify the best course of action.
